{"tid":2392352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭大陣仗巡深水埗 市民嗌「柒婆」迎接","createTime":"2021-02-02T17:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T08:32:54.000Z","uid":242537,"like":416,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"db7e07771c07ccf3cd3a5f5e878311485ed039ff","tid":2392352,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"#突襲封區<br />\n林鄭大陣仗巡深水埗 市民嗌「柒婆」迎接<br />\n<br />\n政府一連兩日突襲封區，行政長官林鄭月娥晚上11時到深水埗大南街視察。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始與民政事務局局長徐英偉一早在場等候迎接，原本正等候檢測的市民亦要暫時讓路。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在逾10人陪同下「遊街」，徐英偉邊行邊講解流動檢測中心安排，林鄭則不時抬頭四處張望，又與兩名長者短暫交談。有記者向林鄭大聲提問「封區成效幾大？」，亦有人高呼「柒婆」，惟她均沒有回應。「巡視」15分鐘後，林鄭即登上坐駕離開。"},{"pid":"fb8d9f9c738737bd28175e3e0a7a8e3129f68caa","tid":2392352,"uid":242537,"like":319,"dislike":0,"score":319,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CGC9eeU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCGC9eeU.jpg&h=80be17e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8c61840b89a4d001a61630fcd596a0f1da26fca","tid":2392352,"uid":242537,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:16:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&amp;v=QqB1uQGFIgc&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fapp%3Ddesktop%26v%3DQqB1uQGFIgc%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=71c1289a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&amp;v=QqB1uQGFIgc&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"26a21e2544236e678a508f1e311947aa49d15db5","tid":2392352,"uid":182244,"like":243,"dislike":0,"score":243,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"不如一齊食扭扭薯條？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b17981c7eaae20cba41b97068133dab4b859d7","tid":2392352,"uid":219007,"like":424,"dislike":0,"score":424,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"蛋蛋記者叫ga : 柒婆望望鏡頭唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\